=9Cblockchain depositary receipts=E2=80=9D on U.S. dollars kept in the trad=
itional financial system.[3] It says: =E2=80=9CMoving between the tradition=
al and crypto worlds is difficult and complicated, so let me handle that fo=
r you.=E2=80=9D (As compensation, it generally gets to keep the interest on=
 the money it keeps in its bank account.)But there is another way, which is=
