ose money, but if they don=E2=80=99t lose too much money the Crypto Bank is=
 fine (it has a senior claim on the Bitcoins) and so the stablecoins are st=
ill worth $1 each.I don=E2=80=99t mean anything by the loan-to-value ratio =
