em into a CDO-squared. If you buy the senior tranche of a CDO-squared you=
=E2=80=99re getting a senior claim (the CDO-squared tranche) on a pool (the=
 CDO-squared)=C2=A0of junior claims (mezzanine CDO tranches) on a pool (the=
