n a pool (the MBS) of senior claims (mortgages) on houses.[2]=C2=A0Just com=
posing the main move.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Actually the=C2=A0<em=
>bank=C2=A0</em>itself is a composition of this move. A bank makes a bunch =
of loans in exchange for senior claims on businesses, houses, etc. Then it =
pools those loans together on its balance sheet and issues a bunch of diffe=
rent claims on them. The most senior claims, classically, are =E2=80=9Cbank=
